name: Swedish International Liberal Center
memberOrga: We are not a membership organisation, but a foundation
goal:
SILC is a liberal foundation that promotes democracy.
Our main goal is to strengthen organizations and individuals in their struggle for democracy and human rights.
interests: Climate Action, Enlargement, European Neighbourhood Policy, External Relations, Foreign affairs and security policy, Humanitarian aid and civil protection, Justice and Fundamental Rights, Trade, Youth
euInitiatives: Foreign policy, especially development policy and policy directed towards authoritarian countries.
